data.description: Welcome to this charming home with beautiful hillside views. This lovely home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, laminate flooring throughout, fireplace in living room, dining area, renovated kitchen with quartz countertops, ample master bedroom with master bath and double doors leading to backyard, oversized one car garage, enclosed bonus room with washer/dryer hookups, covered patio, shed in backyard, and large back yard.  Easy access to shopping, schools, parks, shopping, downtown Riverside, UC Riverside, and much more!
